NAME

DateTime::Locale::mfe_MU - Locale data examples for the Morisyen Mauritius (mfe-MU) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Morisyen Mauritius locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mardi 5 fevriye 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vandredi 22 desam 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = samdi 15 septam -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 fevriye 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 desam 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 septam -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 fev, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 des, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 sep, -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10
